name: Advertising experiment #10
description: This is an advertising experiment. Owners of this OBJKT will be listed as "featured user" on the exploration tool https://projects.stroep.nl/hicetnunc/ until 28/06/2021. On each page view the featured user is randomly chosen. The data will be fetched using the API from https://better-call.dev, so once collected the collector should be featured directly. If you collect more, you get featured more often, but it's also possible to sell it on secondary market during the week or give to friends!
